{"tid":828050,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真係小氣？C朗取消關注拉莫斯IG","createTime":"2018-09-19T11:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T12:20:29.000Z","uid":20634,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7422ba963b3074f79058886716b41b9470063d1b","tid":828050,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180917/photo/bkn-20180917110328592-0917_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180917113312\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180917%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180917110328592-0917_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180917113312&h=c24ee031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯喺意甲主場以2:1擊敗薩斯索羅，C朗包辦兩個入球當然開心，不過有傳媒發現，原來C朗嘅Instagram已經取消關注部分皇家馬德里球員，包括同佢<span style=\"color: red;\">並肩作戰多年</span>嘅沙治奧拉莫斯，懷疑佢又玩小氣。<br />\n<br />\nC朗<span style=\"color: red;\">臨時甩底</span>冇出席歐聯分組賽抽籤儀式，據講原因係，佢知道自己失落上季歐聯最佳球員大獎，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">嬲豬玩失蹤</span>，點知話口未完，傳媒又踢爆佢取消關注沙治奧拉莫斯、丹尼爾卡華積、丹尼施巴路斯同馬里安奴戴亞斯，懷疑佢<span style=\"color: red;\">玩小氣</span>同皇馬割席。<br />\n<br />\n雖然C朗嘅IG依然有關注莫迪歷同馬些路，但傳媒覺得佢因為嬲皇馬唔挽留佢，已經對銀河艦隊死心，加上沙治奧拉莫斯喺歐聯分組賽抽籤儀式上，疑似更支持莫迪歷當選世界足球先生，又暗踩C朗鍾意借網上輿論造勢，結果咪搞成咁囉！"},{"pid":"222172bdd9f27156b85292f2442ef42b06d19dea","tid":828050,"uid":59664,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"洗撚俾面牆頭草臭閪"},{"pid":"d4ff3832256f03db3b0b9420a29e3a9fa1277513","tid":828050,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"真愛馬些路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0531b1acb15438fbce4c4494e0fb2bdb028376f","tid":828050,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"我要走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你咪走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a49d1218c70867a4d94691295e08a75b690a81e","tid":828050,"uid":109523,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:47:50.000Z","msg":"拉莫狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc50460b6f4c1ab885b2489f35ce263ecea9dc5","tid":828050,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d456af72f754754321b884bd2fa4626597e71f9","tid":828050,"uid":58811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心機，會幫手highlight重點方便大家速讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 騎哥要學下"},{"pid":"598664f8196bb5be1d8f62359f97830cf9816e3d","tid":828050,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"la concha de tu madre<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}